originalText.text: I always enjoy beautiful objects created by beautiful and talented Stephanie. It became a tradition for our family to purchase jewelry from this creative designer. We wish her all the best!

originalText.text: Absolutely gorgeous jewelry with exquisite attention to detail and use of color. Each piece is so beautiful to look at, touch, and experience. Stephanie is a true artist and I'm so happy that my girls and I own pieces of her work!

originalText.text: Stephanie Dubsky's pieces are so unique and beautiful. I had so much fun finding treasures at her open studio, trying on rings that felt so comfortable on my fingers and deciding which bowls were the prettiest. I came for gifts and found it very challenging not to get something for me! Thank you Stephanie!

originalText.text: These earrings are beautiful.  The quality is great.  They were shipped immediately and arrived quickly in time for the holidays.  This is an extraordinary artist.  She ships quickly.  You will not be disappointed.

originalText.text:
Beautiful art in the guise of jewelry. Or vice versa. Stephanie's gift is clear online but to enter her world and experience her artistry is just beyond delight.

Thoughtful and gorgeous with that perfect feeling of mass. The piece was glorious but the people - Stephanie - made the experience a true joy.

Her abilities reflect her disposition. Beauty equals beauty.

I love her work! So will you.

My Mrs too! Love. Love. Love.
